---
title: Easy Sheet Pan Chicken Dinner with Broccoli, Tomatoes and Cheesy Bread
description: This one-pan wonder is full of big Italian-inspired flavours! Chicken and veggies are roasted together with a zesty DIY dressing. Dunk the easy-cheesy herb bread in the delicious pan juices.
